  "Cal Baptist":{ vibe:"fire", ceiling:"Round of 32", strengths:["WAC Tournament champions","Jamion Christian: first-year coach, elite energy","Guard-heavy attack that creates open looks"], weaknesses:["WAC competition is significantly below Big 12","Kansas has the #1 NBA Draft pick — talent gap is real","Must sustain tournament momentum against elite opponent"], stats:[{val:"25-8",lbl:"Record"},{val:"WAC",lbl:"Tournament champions"},{val:"13-seed",lbl:"Historically 4% upset rate"}], players:[{name:"Guard corps",stat:"WAC's most dynamic backcourt"}], vibeDesc:"Cal Baptist won the WAC Tournament in dramatic fashion — they missed a tying alley-oop at the buzzer but had already put the game away. First-year head coach Jamion Christian has this team playing with an edge. They're the hottest mid-major no one's talking about." },
  "Louisville":{ vibe:"shaky", ceiling:"Round of 32", strengths:["Pat Kelsey has elevated this program rapidly","Chucky Brown Jr. can erupt for 25+ on any night","Physical frontcourt can bully smaller teams"], weaknesses:["Mikel Brown Jr. questionable (back injury) — their best two-way player","Top-25 in 3PA allowed — South Florida will test them","Lost 4 of last 7 entering tournament"], stats:[{val:"Mikel Brown Jr.",lbl:"Questionable — back injury"},{val:"Top 25",lbl:"3PA allowed nationally"},{val:"22-10",lbl:"Record"}], players:[{name:"Chucky Brown Jr.",stat:"Explosive scorer — can go for 25+ any night"},{name:"Mikel Brown Jr.",stat:"Best defender — injury status is the whole story"}], vibeDesc:"Pat Kelsey has Louisville trending up but this team has a critical injury concern: Mikel Brown Jr. is questionable with a back issue. Without their best defender, they're matchup bait for a South Florida squad that launches threes at will. The Cards have the talent — if Brown plays, this is a coin flip." },
